# Public export allowlist.
#
# This repository is intentionally a small public slice of the private Scholay
# codebase. Ignore everything first, then explicitly re-include the files that
# are safe to publish.
*

# Public root files
!.gitignore
!LICENSE
!README.md
!/assets/
!/assets/readme-hero.svg

# Public skill directories
!/corpus-building/
!/corpus-building/**
!/evidence-review/
!/evidence-review/**
!/literature-discovery/
!/literature-discovery/**
!/research-writing/
!/research-writing/**
!/source-intake/
!/source-intake/**

# Never publish local/editor files, credentials, generated output, or private
# source drops even if they are copied here by accident.
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*secret*
*credential*
*token*
node_modules/
dist/
build/
coverage/
.cache/
.turbo/
*.log
tmp/
temp/
/scholay-agent-skills/
/backend/
/frontend-admin/
/frontend-user/
/agent/
